		<title>C/2020 F3 (NEOWISE) が見頃</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://text.baldanders.info/remark/2020/07/comet-neowise/" />
		<id>tag:text.Baldanders.info,2020-07-12:/remark/2020/07/comet-neowise/</id>
		<published>2020-07-12T03:30:53+00:00</published>
		<updated>2020-08-16T01:53:46+00:00</updated>
		<summary>私は朝が弱いので，明け方の天文イベントはダメダメなんだよなぁ orz</summary>
		<author>
			<name>Spiegel</name>
			<uri>https://baldanders.info/profile/</uri>
		</author>
		
	<link rel="cc:license" type="application/rdf+xml" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/rdf" />


		<content type="html" xml:lang="ja" xml:base="https://text.baldanders.info/">&lt;p&gt;2020年3月に &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/neowise/main/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; title=&#34;NEOWISE | NASA&#34;&gt;NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt; によって発見された彗星 C/2020 F3 (NEOWISE) が明け方の東の空で見頃になっているらしい。
私は朝が弱いので，明け方の天文イベントはダメダメなんだよなぁ &lt;code&gt;orz&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ちうわけで記念に記事を残しておく。
以下は ISS から見た NEOWISE 彗星だそうだ。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure style=&#39;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;&#39;&gt;
&lt;blockquote class=&#34;nobox&#34; cite=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yh1_wHdUx3Y&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; margin: 0 2rem; padding-bottom: 56.25%; padding-top: 30px; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;
&lt;iframe class=&#34;youtube-player&#34; style=&#34;position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;&#34; allowfullscreen frameborder=&#34;0&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Yh1_wHdUx3Y&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;q&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yh1_wHdUx3Y&#34;&gt;Comet NEOWISE from ISS - YouTube&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/q&gt;より&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;この動画の3分過ぎあたりから NEOWISE 彗星が昇ってくる。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;また “&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Astronomy Picture of the Day&lt;/a&gt;” でも NEOWISE 彗星の画像が連日アップされている。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200707.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 7 - Comet NEOWISE over Lebanon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200709.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 9 - Noctilucent NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200710.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 10 - Comet NEOWISE from the ISS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200711.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 11 - The Tails of Comet NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure style=&#39;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;&#39;&gt;
&lt;blockquote class=&#34;nobox&#34; cite=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ts0Ek3nLHew&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; margin: 0 2rem; padding-bottom: 56.25%; padding-top: 30px; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;
&lt;iframe class=&#34;youtube-player&#34; style=&#34;position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;&#34; allowfullscreen frameborder=&#34;0&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/ts0Ek3nLHew&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;q&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ts0Ek3nLHew&#34;&gt;Comet NEOWISE Rising over the Adriatic Sea - YouTube&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/q&gt;より&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt; &lt;!-- APOD: 2020 July 13 --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200714.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 14 - Comet NEOWISE over Stonehenge&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200715.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 15 - Comet NEOWISE over the Swiss Alps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200716.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 16 - The Long Tails of Comet NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200717.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 17 - NEOWISE of the North&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200718.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 18 - Finding NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200720.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 20 - Comet NEOWISE and Nebulae&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200722.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 22 – The Structured Tails of Comet NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200723.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 23 - Fairytale NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200724.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 24 - MAGIC NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200727.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 July 27 – Comet and Lightning Beyond Bighorn Mountains&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apod.nasa.gov/apod/ap200812.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;APOD: 2020 August 12 - The Shifting Tails of Comet NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ちなみに &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/neowise/main/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; title=&#34;NEOWISE | NASA&#34;&gt;NEOWISE&lt;/a&gt; は NASA の WISE (Wide-field Infrared Survey Explorer) 宇宙望遠鏡を使って地球近傍天体（Near-Earth Object; NEO）を捜索するためのミッションおよび宇宙機を指している。
ちゃんと仕事して成果を出してるわけやね。&lt;/p&gt;
